This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation and translation. The use of deep learning models also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of multiple modalities and medical applications suggests that it could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) suggests that it could belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
